Depends: R(>= 4.2), methods, igraph, ggplot2
Imports: scales, grid
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, RUnit, BiocGenerics, BiocStyle, PathwaySpace, RedeR
Description: GraphSpace is an R package that integrates igraph and ggplot2 graphics within a spatial map. GraphSpace implements new geometric objects using ggplot2 protypes, customized for representing large igraph objects in a normalized coordinate system.
